# Full Project Audit & Restructuring Plan

## Problem

The repo-evolution-pipeline has **two parallel systems** ‚Äî a V1 LangGraph prototype and a V2 orchestrator ‚Äî with duplicated models, broken cross-references, and 15+ schema mismatches preventing the pipeline from running.

