### üî¥ Delete (V1 Legacy Dead Code ‚Äî 12 files)

These files are **never imported by the V2 pipeline** and use a completely different state system ([graph/state.py](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/graph/state.py) TypedDict vs [pipeline/core/models.py](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/core/models.py) Pydantic).

| File | Reason for Deletion |
|------|---------------------|
