| [agents/ci_builder.py](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/agents/ci_builder.py) | V1 CI builder ‚Äî uses `graph.state.PipelineState` |
| [agents/doc_writer.py](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/agents/doc_writer.py) | V1 doc writer ‚Äî uses `graph.state.PipelineState` |
| [graph/state.py](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/graph/state.py) | V1 state schema ‚Äî separate TypedDict models |
