### üü° Fix (Remaining Bug List)

#### 1. [models.py](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/core/models.py) ‚Äî Add missing fields and enum values

| Issue | Fix |
|-------|-----|
| [RepoManifest](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/core/models.py#71-90) missing `topics` | Add `topics: list[str] = Field(default_factory=list)` |
| [RepoCategory](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/core/models.py#17-24) missing `DASHBOARD`, `ECOMMERCE`, `SOCIAL`, `BLOG`, `DOCS`, `API` | Add these enum members (used by architect) |
| [QualityGate](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/core/models.py#164-171) missing [passed](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/tests/test_models.py#95-105), `message`, `weight`, `is_critical` | Add these fields (used by tests and gates logic) |

#### 2. [codegen.py](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/agents/codegen.py) ‚Äî Invalid `model=` kwarg

Same bug as analyzer had ‚Äî uses `model=config.llm.codegen_model` which doesn't exist. Fix: use `heavy=True`.

#### 3. [__main__.py](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/__main__.py) ‚Äî Quality command references

Line 128 uses `NavigationType.TABS` (already fixed via alias) but also constructs objects in [cmd_quality()](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/__main__.py#106-147) that may hit other schema issues.

#### 4. [conftest.py](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/tests/conftest.py) ‚Äî Test fixtures misaligned

- [sample_manifest](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/tests/conftest.py#16-29) uses `topics=["portfolio", "react", "nextjs"]` (needs field added to model)
- [sample_deep_analysis](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/tests/conftest.py#60-75) uses `data_models=["Project", "ContactForm"]` (strings, needs list[dict] fix or flexible field)
- [sample_architecture](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/tests/conftest.py#77-98) uses [ScreenSpec(name="Home", purpose=..., components=...)](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/core/models.py#135-148) (already fixed)

#### 5. [test_models.py](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/tests/test_models.py) ‚Äî Tests use missing fields

- [QualityGate(passed=True, message="...", weight=10, is_critical=True)](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/core/models.py#164-171) ‚Äî fields don't exist
- [RepoManifest](file:///Users/mkazi/GitLab%20Mobile%20/repo-evolution-pipeline/pipeline/core/models.py#71-90) test asserts `m.topics == []` ‚Äî field missing

